deck: Smitty is a Woodbury resident.
description:
Made To Suffer

Smitty participates in the prison assault, and ends up killing Billy Greene point blank, and immediately starts mourning for him and regretting his actions. The Governor consoles him by telling him to not regret what he did, reminding him of how many of their own Billy had killed. Smitty wipes the tears from his face and continues shooting the prison survivors.
name: Smitty

deck: Paul is a resident of the Alexandria Safe-Zone.
description:
Call To Arms

Paul shoots Marco in the leg, exclaiming that he believes that Marco is a Whisperer, as he has never seen him before. Jesus restrains him, while Eugene grabs the gun away from Paul. Jesus then tells Paul that the man he shot was Marco and that he was from the Hilltop. Paul is stunned to find out he shot an innocent man. Rick talks to Paul and he explains that he was terrified and on edge after Alpha snuck in during the fair. He says he panicked and thought he was keeping everyone safe by shooting Marco.
name: Paul
